{"type":"text","timestamp":1783411832188,"sessionID":"ses_0c45f6251ffet2WmHVFHB9xYgG","part":{"id":"prt_f3ba0f1e2001kMKwmxM9zQbKo8","messageID":"msg_f3ba0e9e7001QNUVNM9TOb2pN1","sessionID":"ses_0c45f6251ffet2WmHVFHB9xYgG","type":"text","text":"```json\n{\n  \"anomaly_ids\": [],\n  \"answer\": \"根据《XX证券授权管理办法》附件二，单笔报销金额大于等于10,000元且小于50,000元的费用报销，必要审批角色为部门总经理。因此，部门总经理审批线起点为10,000元（含），即单笔金额达到10,000元时即需部门总经理审批。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\", \"clause_no\": \"第二条\"},\n    {\"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\", \"clause_no\": \"附件二\"}\n  ]\n}\n```","time":{"start":1783411831266,"end":1783411832132}}}
